            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Skip the loop by using the <code>autopilotOn</code> variable inside the condition.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Autopilot on: vroom!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"41\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>autopilotOn</code>.</p></body></html>"
